metadata.description: Proof of Attendance first Cryptovoxels auction 29th February 2020. You were part of making history in Cryptovoxels. This symbolizes that you are early adopters, first users to adopt a new technology before the majority of the population does. In art it is referred to as the Avant-garde, what better name not to give it here where NFT is the Avant-garde of both art and technology
metadata.name: Avant-garde (Proof of Attendance first Cryptovoxels auction)
